overview: Luna Park Ride is the third live album released by the Finnish soprano Tarja Turunen. The concert was filmed at Stadium Luna Park in Buenos Aires, Argentina on the 27th. of March 2011 by fans and mixed by Tim Palmer. Set-List: 1. Dark Star / 2. My Little Phoenix / 3. The Crying Moon / 4. I Walk Alone / 5. Falling Awake / 6. Signos / 7. Little Lies / 8. Underneath / 9. Stargazers / 10. Ciaran's Well / 11. In For a Kill / 12. Where Were You Last Night / Heaven is a Place on Earth / Livin' on a Prayer (Medley) / 13. Die Alive / 14. Until My Last Breath / 15. Wishmaster.
title: Tarja - Luna Park Ride
